&lt;p&gt;The Sales Manager is Paystand’s front-line commercial leader for LatAm — the person responsible for building a high-performing sales team, driving consistent revenue results, and personally closing complex deals. This is not a purely managerial role: the Sales Manager leads from the front, carrying their own quota while owning the collective performance of a team of 4–6 Account Executives.&lt;/p&gt;
