&lt;p&gt;The Senior Accountant is responsible for maintaining the General Ledger (GL), performing month-end close activities, and preparing financial reports. This role requires a high degree of accuracy, strong analytical skills, and proactive communication across English- and Spanish-speaking teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Beyond core accounting expertise, this role is ideal for someone who is genuinely excited about using AI and automation to improve financial workflows — whether that means building smarter reconciliation processes, automating routine reporting, or finding new ways to surface insights faster.&lt;/p&gt;
