&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Paystand&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It’s about time we reboot commercial finance.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For the past century, business payments have lagged behind the rest of the digital enterprise — held back by fees, fragmented systems, manual workflows, and paper-driven processes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Paystand was created to change that.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We eliminate transaction fees, digitize the cash cycle, and help businesses create a self-driving money experience across AR, AP, FX, Bitwage, mining, USDb, AI, and emerging global financial infrastructure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As Paystand enters its next stage of growth, our products, acquisitions, markets, customer base, and global footprint are expanding quickly. We need a senior corporate marketing leader who can turn that complexity into one clear, powerful, market-facing story.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is built for a scrappy, resilient, high-agency operator who thrives in disruption, moves quickly through ambiguity, and is energized by helping redefine the future of commercial finance.&lt;/p&gt;
