&lt;p&gt;This leader will own Paystand’s corporate narrative, brand architecture, executive communications, public relations, analyst relations, thought leadership, strategic events, employer brand, customer storytelling, and company-level messaging across the Group.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The mandate is to help Paystand show up as one company across products, geographies, acquisitions, customers, partners, candidates, investors, analysts, and employees.&lt;/p&gt;
